<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- tftkr hạtrwḥ lfyn .. ylly mạsẖy fy sktyn

[V2]
 mstḥyl ạ̉bdạaⁿ hạtwṣl .. dạ ạ̹nt mqswm ḥttyn

[V3]
 ywm fy nʿmẗ wywm fy nạr .. ạ̹nt kẖạṭy wlạ bạr

[V4]
 ạ̹nt ạ̉byḍ wlạ ạ̹swd .. wlạ bạrd wlạ ḥạr

[V5]
 ạlqrạr - kẖd qrạr .. ạ̹nt lyh wlạ ʿlyh .. ạ̹nt ṣạḥb ạlạ̹kẖtyạr

[V6]
 kẖd qrạr .. msẖ hạynfʿ nwr wḍlmh .. dy ạlḥyạẗ zy ạlbkẖạr

[V7]
 msẖ hạynfʿ tmsẖy skh .. fy ạlnhạyẗ mwt wnạr

[V8]
 qwlh bkẖtạrk bḥbk .. hạbqy mlkk bạ̹ftkẖạr

[V9]
 2- mrkbk dy brysyn .. wạlḥyạẗ fyhạ mḥạl

[V10]
 bṣ sẖwf ạ̉yạm mạḍyk .. ywm ymyn wywm sẖmạl

[V11]
 mtḥạwlsẖ tbạn sʿyd .. wạ̹nt ʿạysẖ fy ạ̹nksạr

[V12]
 ạ̹nt kẖạyf wlạ ʿạrf .. bs msẖ ạ̉d ạlqrạr

[V13]
 3- wfyh bạb ḍyq wṣʿb .. wṭryqh mlyạn mrạr

[V14]
 dh ạlly fy nhạyth ạlḥyạẗ .. wạlfrḥ wạlạ̹ntṣạr</lyrics>
<title>kẖd qrạr</title>
